\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
I. Ga\u353\'61parovi\u269\'0d, poslanec: }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
P\u225\'e1n predseda vl\u225\'e1dy, bolo zauj\u237\'edmav\u233\'e9 v\u225\'e1s po\u269\'0d\u250\'fava\u357\'65, ale nie preto, \u382\'7ee va\u353\'61a argument\u225\'e1cia jednozna\u269\'0dne preukazovala va\u353\'61u snahu a v\u253\'fdsledky pozit\u237\'edva. Bolo v\u225\'e1s zauj\u237\'edmav\u233\'e9 po\u269\'0d\u250\'fava\u357\'65 preto, ako ste n\u225\'e1m poslancom v N\u225\'e1rodnej rade e\u353\'61te teraz hovorili, \u269\'0do m\u225\'e1me robi\u357\'65 a kde sme my zlyhali. Bolo zauj\u237\'edmav\u233\'e9, ke\u271\'0f ste povedali, \u382\'7ee p\u225\'e1n Cuper to berie na \u318\'3eahk\u250\'fa v\u225\'e1hu. Ja si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee na \u318\'3eah\u353\'61iu v\u225\'e1hu, ako to beriete vy a va\u353\'61a vl\u225\'e1da, to u\u382\'7e nikto zobra\u357\'65 nemohol. Ve\u271\'0f ke\u271\'0f u\u382\'7e ni\u269\'0d in\u233\'e9, tak len z\u225\'e1kladn\u225\'e1 zmluva o priate\u318\'3estve s Ma\u271\'0farskom, ktor\u225\'e1 bola prijat\u225\'e1, hovor\u237\'ed jednozna\u269\'0dne, ak jedna \u269\'0di druh\u225\'e1 strana m\u225\'e1 v \u250\'famysle \u237\'eds\u357\'65 nad r\u225\'e1mec tejto zmluvy, treba predt\u253\'fdm rokova\u357\'65. Vy ste nerokovali. Ak pova\u382\'7eujete tie rokovania, \u269\'0do ste tu \u269\'0d\u237\'edtali, \u382\'7ee v\u225\'e1s aj citovala ma\u271\'0farsk\u225\'e1 tla\u269\'0d, tak to je tak, ako ke\u271\'0f sa stretneme pri poh\u225\'e1riku a povieme si: Ty, Jano, nerob to! Ofici\u225\'e1lne stretnutie je nie\u269\'0do \u250\'faplne in\u233\'e9. A to ste neurobili. To ste neurobili. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
A po druh\u233\'e9, p\u225\'e1n premi\u233\'e9r, upozor\u328\'48ujete n\u225\'e1s na term\u237\'edny. Ak\u233\'e9 term\u237\'edny? Pri tejto pr\u237\'edle\u382\'7eitosti by som sa v\u225\'e1s r\u225\'e1d op\u253\'fdtal a\~povedzte: O ak\u253\'fdch term\u237\'ednoch to hovor\u237\'edte? A \u269\'0do tie term\u237\'edny bud\u250\'fa znamena\u357\'65? Ni\u269\'0d. Ak to ma\u271\'0farsk\u225\'e1 strana neprijme, \u269\'0do urob\u237\'edte? \u8211\'13 to je moja ot\u225\'e1zka. Preto\u382\'7ee nevid\u237\'edm, skuto\u269\'0dne nevid\u237\'edm pozit\u237\'edva vo va\u353\'61ej pr\u225\'e1ci. Vykrikova\u357\'65 pozde, to u\u382\'7e nepom\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee, to je sk\u244\'f4r na \u353\'61kodu v tomto \u269\'0dase. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5

