M. Podhradsk\u225\'e1, poslanky\u328\'48a: }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
\u270\'0eakujem za slovo, p\u225\'e1n predseda. P\u225\'e1n premi\u233\'e9r, pou\u382\'7eili ste nieko\u318\'3eko ve\u318\'3emi pozoruhodn\u253\'fdch viet vo va\u353\'61om vyst\u250\'fapen\u237\'ed. Obvinili ste n\u225\'e1s napr\u237\'edklad, \u382\'7ee zosmie\u353\'61\u328\'48ujeme t\u233\'e9mu. A nie je to dobr\u233\'e9. Nu\u382\'7e, p\u225\'e1n premi\u233\'e9r, ak niekto zosmie\u353\'61\u328\'48uje t\u233\'e9mu, tak ste to predov\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdm vy, ale trag\u233\'e9diou je, \u382\'7ee nezosmie\u353\'61\u328\'48ujete len t\u250\'fato v\u225\'e1\u382\'7enu t\u233\'e9mu, ale vy zosmie\u353\'61\u328\'48ujete cel\u233\'e9 Slovensko v o\u269\'0diach svetovej verejnosti. A to u\u382\'7e s\u250\'fa naozaj ve\u318\'3emi v\u225\'e1\u382\'7ene veci. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
Hovorili ste, aby sme boli prezierav\u237\'ed a pokojn\u237\'ed a racion\u225\'e1lne rie\u353\'61ili cel\u253\'fd probl\u233\'e9m. Jeden z\~va\u353\'61ich argumentov bol aj ten, \u382\'7ee v Ma\u271\'0farsku bud\u250\'fa vo\u318\'3eby. Nu\u382\'7e, je to ve\u318\'3emi pre\u269\'0dudesn\u233\'e9 pochopenie, ktor\u233\'e9 prejavujete vo\u269\'0di ma\u271\'0farskej strane, ak sa odvol\u225\'e1vate pr\u225\'e1ve na bl\u237\'ed\u382\'7eiace sa vo\u318\'3eby. Lebo ak by bl\u237\'ed\u382\'7eiace sa vo\u318\'3eby a tento z\u225\'e1kon, o ktorom tu hovor\u237\'edme, tento kontroverzn\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1kon mal by by\u357\'65 tou podmienkou, aby sa v Ma\u271\'0farsku ujala vl\u225\'e1dy vl\u225\'e1da, ktor\u225\'e1 bude rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 veci rozumn\u253\'fdm sp\u244\'f4sobom, tak tu nie\u269\'0do nesed\u237\'ed. Nie\u269\'0do nie je v Ma\u271\'0farsku v poriadku, ak by ma\u271\'0farsk\u225\'e1 vl\u225\'e1da, ke\u271\'0f prijme na\u353\'61e v\u253\'fdhrady vo\u269\'0di z\u225\'e1konu, prehrala u voli\u269\'0dov. Vy vlastne v Ma\u271\'0farsku podporujete sily, ktor\u233\'e9 maj\u250\'fa \u271\'0faleko od demokratick\u253\'fdch sna\u382\'7een\u237\'ed, ktor\u233\'e9 presadzuje cel\u225\'e1 Eur\u243\'f3pa a Eur\u243\'f3pska \u250\'fania. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
A e\u353\'61te jednu vec. Varovali ste slovensk\u253\'fd parlament, aby v\u225\'e1m nevyty\u269\'0doval \u382\'7eiadne term\u237\'edny a nevyty\u269\'0doval priestor. Je to smie\u353\'61ne, ke\u271\'0f varujete slovensk\u253\'fd parlament. Ak v\u225\'e1m niekto vyt\u253\'fd\u269\'0dil priestor a term\u237\'edny, bol to ma\u271\'0farsk\u253\'fd parlament. Ale zd\u225\'e1 sa, \u382\'7ee to v\u225\'e1m neprek\u225\'e1\u382\'7ea. V slovenskom parlamente sa dovol\u225\'e1vate pochopenia, ale ke\u271\'0f m\u225\'e1te vyjedn\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 kv\u244\'f4li tomuto z\u225\'e1konu s Ma\u271\'0farmi, tak ste neuverite\u318\'3ene \u250\'fastup\u269\'0div\u253\'fd a hovor\u237\'edte o tom, \u382\'7ee uplat\u328\'48ujete kultivovan\u250\'fa diplomaciu. P\u225\'e1n premi\u233\'e9r, va\u353\'61a diplomacia u\u382\'7e d\u225\'e1vno zlyhala a mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee Slovensko to vie. (Zaznel zvuk \u269\'0dasomiery.)}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5

