\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
K t\u253\'fdm ot\u225\'e1zkam fungovania kancel\u225\'e1ri\u237\'ed, predpoklad\u225\'e1m, sa vyjadr\u237\'ed p\u225\'e1n minister \u352\'60imko. Ten to urob\u237\'ed kvalifikovanej\u353\'61ie, ako by som to urobil ja. To je koniec koncov jedin\u225\'e1 vec, o ktorej hovor\u237\'edte, \u382\'7ee t\u253\'fdm sa nejako realizuje alebo napl\u328\'48uje ten z\u225\'e1kon o Ma\u271\'0faroch v susedn\u253\'fdch \u353\'61t\u225\'e1toch. }
