\par \pard\plain \s24\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi0\ltrpar\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi708{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
1. v\~s\u250\'falade s\~eur\u243\'f3pskym \u353\'61tandardom m\u225\'e1 prim\u225\'e1rnu zodpovednos\u357\'65 za ochranu pr\u225\'e1v men\u353\'61\u237\'edn ich domovsk\u253\'fd \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t;}
\par \pard\plain \s24\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi0\ltrpar\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi708{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
2. ochrana men\u353\'61\u237\'edn zo strany tzv. matersk\u233\'e9ho \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu (Ma\u271\'0farska) sa nesmie t\u253\'fdka\u357\'65 t\u253\'fdch oblast\u237\'ed, ktor\u233\'e9 s\u250\'fa rie\u353\'61en\u233\'e9 dvojstrann\u253\'fdmi zmluvami. \u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee budape\u353\'61tiansky z\u225\'e1kon poru\u353\'61uje dohody o\~ochrane men\u353\'61\u237\'edn zakotven\u233\'e9 v\~Zmluve o\~dobr\u253\'fdch susedsk\u253\'fdch vz\u357\'65ahoch a\~priate\u318\'3eskej spolupr\u225\'e1ci medzi SR a\~MR z\~roku 1995;}
\par \pard\plain \s24\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi0\ltrpar\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi708{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
3. mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tov prij\u237\'edma\u357\'65 jednostrann\u233\'e9 opatrenia vo vz\u357\'65ahu k\~men\u353\'61in\u225\'e1m v\~susedn\u253\'fdch \u353\'61t\u225\'e1toch je podmienen\u225\'e1 re\u353\'61pektovan\u237\'edm princ\u237\'edpov teritori\u225\'e1lnej suverenity \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu, pacta sunt servanda, priate\u318\'3esk\u253\'fdch vz\u357\'65ahov medzi \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tmi a\~re\u353\'61pektovan\u237\'ed \u318\'3eudsk\u253\'fdch pr\u225\'e1v a\~z\u225\'e1kladn\u253\'fdch slob\u244\'f4d;}
\par \pard\plain \s24\qj\widctlpar\faauto\li360\ri0\lin360\rin0\fi0\ltrpar\dbch\af7\dbch\af10\afs24\alang1025\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi708{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f5
